Title: Object: "The Mummy,"
Description: Music cover sheet: a group of men and women looking at a mummy, lying on a pedestal lettered with 'From Thebes / with care / the top side up'; an Egyptian woman standing with arms crossed at centre, in front of an open door lettered with 'Egyptian Court.'. Chromolithograph
Acquisition notes: Purchased from Mr W.G.Imeson of Leigham Vale, SW2
